# Requires:
# - direnv (https://direnv.net)
# - nix-direnv (https://github.com/nix-community/nix-direnv)

watch_file nix/flake.nix nix/parts/
# Use `path:` instead of `.` so that uncommitted changes to flake.nix
# are picked up immediately without requiring a commit.
# Only the `nix/` directory is copied to the Nix store, not the entire repo.
use flake path:./nix
